                    <div class="well" style="background: #E0E0DD; font-size: 16px">
                        <text style="color: black; height:min; padding-bottom:20px; font-size:18px; line-height: 75%">This script organizes your finder windows cascading down and to the right from the top left corner of the screen.<br/><br/>TODO: Select the current front window instead of just finder</br>
